






@(1-9=c269a.1) O @wDN{An}, strengthen the foundations of the throne of life. @wRN{Rīm-@wDN{Sîn}}, may your name be called by a name of life; may he look upon you with favourable eyes, and pay attention to you.
$ (1 line unclear)
May he determine a destiny of life as a fate for you. @wRN{Rīm-@wDN{Sîn}}, may you be beloved of @wDN{An}, and may your kingship endure forever. Great @wDN{An}, make him shepherd of the numerous people.



